Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.database.road

Class Way

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.database.road.Way
  • public class Way
extends Object
    This represents a number of edges in the network graph. This is the representation of (street) edges in OSM and only here for convenience if we need a back reference to the original data. Please use connections for routing algorithms. This is NOT intended for representing anything else then streets!
